Apr 16, 2020
Strategy to open long/short positions based on the crossing of 2 different moving averages. Both moving averages are highly configurable: length, source, and moving average type can be changed.
Apr 16, 2020
Release Notes
Added date filter, default average changed from SMA to EMA
